column5: If you are traveling on Hwy 29 in Wisconsin on your way north,the Abbyland truckstop a few miles west of Abbotsford has great breakfasts. Although it is just a few hours from home it is one of our rituals.A peppered bacon omlet means we are truly on our way to Canada once again.
Our stop is always the Norske Nook in Rice Lake. I'll be eating there Wednesday morning.
